data.description: Welcome to 734 Crosspoint Drive! A large home on a large lot in the quiet subdivision of Northwest Crossing. Equal distance from both San Antonio and South Austin - this is a great commuter home. As you walk through the front door, you are greeted by an open floor plan with living room, dining room and an eat-in kitchen. Upstairs holds 3 bedrooms and a loft. The over-sized primary en-suite boasts dual walk-in closets. This home is perfectly situated for both Texas natives and recent transplants; In-and-Out and Bucee's are only 5 minutes away.
